| Level | Use For |
|-------|---------|
| WHISPER | LOW energy backgrounds only |
| SOFT | Background layers, LOW/MED sections |
| MED | Default balanced presence |
| STRONG | Motion emphasis, HIGH energy |
| PEAK | Single focal moment only (1 group max) |

